hopobject.body: How would you like the money? elite test 360 before and after There are also specialisms within broader themes such as the exploitation of shale gas within the energy theme. Another is the evolution of specialised materials that could transform existing processes such as the manufacture of computers or aircraft. Coutts, the private bank, has been highlighting the potential profits to derive from graphene, a “super material” originally developed in Britain from carbon and with potential applications in flexible screen monitors and elsewhere.
